public class TamerApplet
extends RLApplet

TamerApplet extends RLApplet's functionality (as does TamerPanel for RLPanel) to (1) include button presses that give reward or control signals, (2) save log data through PHP from remote browsers, (3) and allow other experimentally important features, like having a PreExpPanel that allows user input before training and a PostExpPanel that gives information after training.
